{"tid":885731,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔敢再投入感情？","createTime":"2018-11-01T14:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T17:53:18.000Z","uid":26765,"like":126,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a91052b682f550e928961f13f27fb56aa83ed3b5","tid":885731,"uid":26765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"曾經以為會天長地久，結果突如其來嘅分手，已經怕了投入感情，係我傻定太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下段感情唔會再太認真<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下個更可愛"},{"pid":"5620fd7c66b3fea80469a09d445e3ecfc9702a25","tid":885731,"uid":26765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"聽緊姐撚 世界未日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d539c7641e80382f61154f7c4d6289b8ac44868","tid":885731,"uid":14374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"到而家都無意欲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7288729630674d720072b6f77d567a595cac3c3f","tid":885731,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"聽住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8aee11a5badbf76b1708e6529947c0992adb98","tid":885731,"uid":216004,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T22:16:01.000Z","msg":"曾經追到手, 可惜沒法挽留<br />\n原來追到係因為打動而唔係真心鍾意, 所以最後都係冇一齊到。<br />\n最近又有機會開始一段感情, 但原來已經冇耐性去維繫, 開始驚再一次會失敗收場。 其實已經唔只一次係咁諗, 唔想再比人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c1505e3a76783f4f182bcb17c8d1a815c52ece","tid":885731,"uid":45061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T22:30:54.000Z","msg":"細細個就話有動力追女仔，畢竟都新鮮嘛<br />\n大大下就覺得呢樣嘢好煩<br />\n特別係你要花好多時間去了解佢係個咩人，值唔值得你去追（當然對方都係）<br />\n最尾會唔會係埋一齊都仲會有好多變數<br />\n諗起都覺得有啲辛苦<br />\n<br />\n利申：前排同左我個ex分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到依家都仲未放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c10a4b6f06a58d8eac58e46e06afa839fd53e88","tid":885731,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔會有下個，非佢不拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25465f90cc6b6deab73714cccb2907060d546f91","tid":885731,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c10a4b6f06a58d8eac58e46e06afa839fd53e88","tid":885731,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔會有下個，非佢不拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:09:21.000Z","msg":"請問巴打諗住點做,追返佢？"},{"pid":"0ad4b11a7fa125de085c6fd15ad822350c51e788","tid":885731,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25465f90cc6b6deab73714cccb2907060d546f91","tid":885731,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c10a4b6f06a58d8eac58e46e06afa839fd53e88","tid":885731,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔會有下個，非佢不拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:09:21.000Z","msg":"請問巴打諗住點做,追返佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:15:14.000Z","msg":"追唔返了，成為人生遺憾算，睇開啲啦，起碼都曾經擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c78834692167f46d1907a730bc1a7aabf588ee","tid":885731,"uid":14374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad4b11a7fa125de085c6fd15ad822350c51e788","tid":885731,